<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>Peeping Tom • Peeping-Tom TV</xh5><p> <i>Peeping Tom—</i>a person who gets (sexual) pleasure, from secretly watching others: Why don’t you tell everyone that Bob is a <u>Peeping Tom</u>? You saw him peeping into Mariah’s bedroom window...</p><p><i>Peeping-Tom TV—</i>said of reality television shows that focus on the personal lives of ordinary people: “Taxi!” is the latest manifestation of <u>Peeping Tom TV</u>, of which Jeremy Beadle is the brand master.</p> </entry>
